title: Golden Ivory - The White Huntress [1954 - UK] Kenya adventure
description:
The White Huntress (1954 - UK)               aka Golden Ivory

Adventure

starring . . . . Robert Urquhart, John Bentley, Susan Stephen
 
http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0051190/


The film was photographed entirely in Kenya, British East Africa. The co-operation of the local authorities in the colony is gratefully acknowledged. The beautiful veldt and exotic animals are the real stars in this tale of a pair of hunters who mix it up with native tribes and dangerous wildlife in a quest for ivory treasure.
